		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<p>
	<br />
<strong>【教你</strong><strong>识</strong><strong>别</strong><strong>硫磺熏枸杞</strong>】<br />
<span id="__kindeditor_bookmark_start_132__" style="display:none;"></span>很多不法商家抓住消费者喜欢光鲜物品的特点，采用硫磺熏蒸枸杞，而使枸杞鲜艳好看。<br />
<br />
<span style="white-space:normal;"><span style="white-space:normal;"><span style="white-space:normal;"><span style="white-space:normal;"></span></span></span></span> 
